description: This file declares exported API functions for the Sys Rro Bstr Object in a system environment, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions, along with licensing and author information.

methods.name: SysCreateRroBstr

methods.name: SysRroBstrCreate

methods.name: SysRroBstrRemove

methods.description: Enrolls objects necessary for the Sys Rro Bstr Object.

methods.name: SysRroBstrInitialize
